instructions: Put the dinner plate on the tablecloth.
Place the fork to the left of the dinner plate, pointed up.
Place the salad fork to the left of the dinner fork, pointed up.
Place the dinner knife next to the dinner plate with blade toward left.
Place the salad knife to the right of the dinner knife with blade toward left.
Place the soup spoon to the right of the salad knife, pointed up.
Place the water glass above and right of the dinner plate.
Place the wine glass to the right of the water glass.
Place the second wine glass to the right of the first wine glass.
Place the coffee cup to the right of the soup spoon.
Place the bread plate above the dinner fork.
Place the butter knife on the bread plate, pointed up and to the left.
Place the dessert fork above the dinner plate, pointing towards the water glass.
Place the dessert spoon above the dessert fork, pointing towards the bread plate.
Place the folded napkin on the dinner plate.
